Plot: The life of a time-traveling Temporal Agent. On his final assignment, he must pursue the one criminal that has eluded him throughout time.
Title: Predestination
Writer: Michael Spierig, Peter Spierig, Robert A. Heinlein (story "All You Zombies")
Actors: Ethan Hawke, Sarah Snook, Christopher Kirby, Christopher Sommers
tomatoConsensus: Fun genre fare with uncommon intelligence, Predestination serves as a better-than-average sci-fi adventure -- and offers a starmaking turn from Sarah Snook.
